{{Top|leg}}
'''ILKO''' was one of the master encrypt codes the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] used to transfer data between [[Coruscant/Legends|Imperial Center]] and the original [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|Death Star]] construction facility at [[Despayre]].

An entire [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance]] team needed a month to break the code; [[Zakarisz Ghent]], a slicer working for [[Talon Karrde]], broke the code single-handedly in two months when he was twelve years old.

ILKO was named for [[Ilko Deminar]],<ref name="CSWE">{{CSWECite|II|83}}</ref> the head of the [[Cryptanalysis Department]] of the [[Senate Bureau of Intelligence/Legends|Senate Bureau of Intelligence]] in the early stages of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]].

